<form class="form-inline my-2 my-lg-0 ml-auto">
    <input
      class="form-control mr-sm-2"
      type="search"
      placeholder="Search Products"
      aria-label="Search"
    />
    <button class="btn btn-outline-light my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit">
      Search
    </button>
  </form>
